data.text: Nancy Ellen Carell (née Walls) is an American actress. She played Carol Stills on The Office. She is also the wife of actor Steve Carell, who plays Michael. She had a cameo in the health center scene in Steve Carell's film The Forty-Year Old Virgin. She also had a brief role in the opening scene of Seeking a Friend for the End of the World as Steve Carell's character's bolting girlfriend, and in Bridesmaids as Helen's tennis partner.
